{"lemma":"غَرْزُ","slug":"غَرْزُ","root":"غ.ر.ز","root_slug":"غ-ر-ز","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ر-ز","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31656","","n31657","n31658"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B2%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to pierce, to prick, to stab"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fasten, to fix, to insert"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lay eggs"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣa.ra.za/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31656","headword_ar":"غَرَزَ","root":"grz","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garozN","text_ar":"غَرْزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He pricked"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing with a needle, (S, K,) and with a stick or the like. (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nxs","text_ar":"نخس"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He inserted"},{"kind":"text","text":"a needle into a thing; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gr~z","text_ar":"غرّز","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he stuck,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fixed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA,) a thing, (Msb,) or a stick, (TA,) into the ground; (Msb, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he inserted and fixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"a stick into the ground; (Mgh;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he planted"},{"kind":"text","text":"a tree; [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garasa","text_ar":"غَرَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] (TA;) with the same aor., (Msb,) and the same inf. n.; (Mgh, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Agrz","text_ar":"اغرز","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b3-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaza rijolahu fY Algarozi","text_ar":"غَرَزَ رِجْلَهُ فى الغَرْزِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY","text_ar":"فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~ikaAbi","text_ar":"الرِّكَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (S,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put his foot into the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoz","text_ar":"غَرْز"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stirrup;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Agtrz","text_ar":"اغترز","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone, from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garozN","text_ar":"غَرْزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning a kind of stirrup]. (A, K.) ―         -b4-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garazati","text_ar":"غَرَزَتِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljaraAdapu","text_ar":"الجَرَادَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gr~zt","text_ar":"غرّزت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gr~zt bi*anabihaA","text_ar":"غرّزت بِذَنَبِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tagoriyzN","text_ar":"تَغْرِيزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The locust stuck her tail into the ground to lay her eggs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) ―         -b5-  And hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqaAma biA^aroDinaA wagaraza *anabahu","text_ar":"اَقَامَ بِاَرْضِنَا وَغَرَزَ ذَنَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stayed."},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abode, in our land, and remained fixed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did not quit it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*nb","text_ar":"ذنب"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guriza","text_ar":"غُرِزَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gur~iza","text_ar":"غُرِّزَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"are also said of anything when one means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was tucked up"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$um~ira","text_ar":"شُمِّرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":") into a thing. (TA.) It is said in a trad. of El-Hasan,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dufura raA^osihi","text_ar":"ضُفُرَ رَاْسِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqado gar~aza","text_ar":"وَقَدْ غَرَّزَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And he had twisted"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the locks"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plaits of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his hair, and inserted its extremities into its roots."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariza","text_ar":"غَرِزَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sgh, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garozN","text_ar":"غَرْزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He obeyed the Sultán after having been disobedient to him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sgh, K:) as though he laid hold of his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoz","text_ar":"غَرْز"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or stirrup] and went with him. (TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garazato","text_ar":"غَرَزَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giraAzN","text_ar":"غِرَازٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garozN","text_ar":"غَرْزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel, S, A, K, and a sheep or goat, and an ass, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had little milk; her milk became little."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","Msb","A","Sgh","TK"]},{"entry_id":"n31657","headword_ar":"غَرْزٌ","root":"grz","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stirrup"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the camel's saddle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made of skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sewed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) that of iron [or brass] or wood being called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rikaAbN","text_ar":"رِكَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camel's stirrup:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) IAar says that"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is to the she-camel like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HizaAm","text_ar":"حِزَام"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the horse:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but others say, that"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is to the camel like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rikaAb","text_ar":"رِكَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the mule."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ailozamo garoza fulaAnK","text_ar":"اِلْزَمْ غَرْزَ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Keep thou to the stirrup of such a one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning,] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"keep thou to the commands and prohibitions of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Au$odudo yadayoka bigarozihi","text_ar":"اُشْدُدْ يَدَيْكَ بِغَرْزِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cleave thou to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and leave him not."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisotamosiko bigarozihi","text_ar":"اِسْتَمْسِكْ بِغَرْزِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cling thou to him, and follow what he says and does, and disobey him not;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as one lays hold upon the stirrup of the rider and goes with him. (TA.)       -A2-  Also sing. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guruwzN","text_ar":"غُرُوزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sprigs ingrafted upon the branches of the grape-vine."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K","Msb","A"]},{"entry_id":"n31658","headword_ar":"غَرَزٌ","root":"grz","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A species of panic grass"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumaAm","text_ar":"ثُمَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"), (K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small, growing upon the banks of rivers, having no leaves, consisting only of sheaths"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaAbiyb","text_ar":"اَنَابِيب"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"set one into another; and it is of the plants called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamoD","text_ar":"حَمْض"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, as some say, the ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of rush called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asal","text_ar":"اَسَل"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spears"},{"kind":"text","text":"are so called as being likened thereto: As says, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a plant which I have seen in the desert, growing in plain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft, tracts of land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its growth is like that of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sweet rush called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*oxir","text_ar":"اـِذْخِر"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the worst of pasture:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) AHn says,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is an unwholesome pasture; for when the she-camel that pastures upon it is slaughtered, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaz","text_ar":"غَرَز"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is found in her stomach separate from the water, not diffused: and it does not beget the cattle strength:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the n. un. is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": it has been erroneously mentioned as being called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Earaz","text_ar":"عَرَز"},{"kind":"text","text":", with the unpointed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E","text_ar":"ع"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]}]}}